title: Joey DeFrancesco - The Best Of Joey DeFrancesco
description:
Joey DeFrancesco - The Best Of Joey DeFrancesco

Joey DeFrancesco (born April 10, 1971) is an American jazz organist. He is a Grammy-nominated artist who has released more than 30 albums, including recordings with jazz legends Miles Davis and Jimmy Smith. In addition to Grammy nominations in 2004 and 2010, DeFrancesco is a 9-time winner of the Down Beat Critics Poll.

Label: Silverwolf Records
Released: 2014
